# Summary
This documentation describes the integration between Osano (a data privacy platform) and Amplitude, enabling automated PII discovery, classification, and subject rights request handling for GDPR/CCPA compliance. The setup requires an Osano Enterprise plan and involves connecting Amplitude's API key and Secret key in the Osano Portal.

